reviewText: My grandson has fallen in love with Jay Jay.  It is nice to be able to get him more dvd's.
I bought this CD for my grandson and on a recent trip he watched it three times before we got him home.  Any Jay Jay CD or video is a great investment with great lessons for young children.

This was a Birthday Gift For a Grandchild.  Everything went perfectly from purchase to delivery.  Thank You

Gordon D French
